{"blogid": "123589409", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "101", "writerCollect": "279", "writerComment": "29", "writerFan": "38", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "1541", "writerName": "盛夏、白泽", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_123589409.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "13125", "writerRankWeekly": "4043", "writerThumb": "574", "writerVisitNum": "636801", "blog_read_count": "34609", "blog_time": "已于 2022-08-28 09:52:31 修改", "blog_title": "VSCode配置C/C++环境并设置终端输出(无脑教程)", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<h2>1. 下载mingw64 和 安装 VSCode</h2>\n<p>mingw64：<a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/\" title=\"mingw64下载地址\">mingw64下载地址</a></p>\n<p>VSCode：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/Download\" title=\"VScode下载地址\">VScode下载地址</a></p>\n<h2>2. 把mingw64/bin路径配置到环境变量</h2>\n<p>找到mingw64/bin/ ，复制路径</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\c5ee539b3a6740328ec0306f36973e68.png\"/></p>\n<p>配置方法：我的电脑右键--&gt;属性--&gt;高级系统设置--&gt;环境变量--&gt;下面系统变量--&gt;找Path--&gt;变量--&gt;新建--&gt;把路径复制上去--确定(如果是一个长串，在最后加一个分号(英文的)，再在后面粘贴路径)</p>\n<h2>3. 打开VScode，安装插件</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\a50b04fdd4494ebe9864dc2d806b9a6f.png\"/></p>\n<ul><li> <p>第一个：搜chinese</p> <p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\14ae848e9a0240b7be55481e1a13c710.png\"/></p> </li><li> <p>第二个：搜Code Runner</p> <p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\41eba2b0d3844aa8be4b934b394032e8.png\"/></p> </li></ul>\n<ul><li> <p>第三个：搜C/C++</p> <p><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\377ea29e74af450991555256e40ddd78.png\"/></p> </li><li> <p>第四个：搜C/C++ Compile Run</p> <img alt=\"\" height=\"205\" src=\"image\\66ccc071617a4f918b068e243a7fade0.png\" width=\"589\"/></li></ul>\n<h2>4. 重启VScode</h2>\n<p>有重启提示，点确定</p>\n<h2>5. 创建C/C++文件，编写代码</h2>\n<p>后缀名为.c或.cpp的文件</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include&lt;iostream&gt;\nusing namespace std;\nint main(){\n   cout&lt;&lt;\"Hello World\"&lt;&lt;endl;\n}</code></pre>\n<h2>6. 右键Run Code就可以运行</h2>\n<p>会有Hello World输出</p>\n<h2>7. 配置终端输出</h2>\n<p>在设置中输入 run code config 找到里面的 run in terminal 打勾即可</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"70\" src=\"image\\fd12d0a5cbc54f5aa841d997d0dc627d.png\" width=\"354\"/></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}